\[\widehat{\text{AUC}}\left(S_{l};d_{g}\right)\frac{1}{|D_{l}^{0}| \left|D_{l}^{1}\right|}\sum_{x_{ij}}\sum_{x_{uv}}\sigma_{\beta}\left(d_{g}(x_{ uv})-d_{g}(x_{ij})\right)\] (8)

